  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">e7038e94a4a14f07bba6dba</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">At JibJab we respect your right to privacy and we understand that you need to control the uses of your personal information This Privacy Policy details below the measures taken by JibJab to protect your privacy in connection with your use of the JibJab Sites However you understand that the JibJab Sites and JibJab Services allow among other things users who are 13 or older to post personal content e g photographs and information about themselves and others for whom they have the authority or permission to post photos and information for public review and comment both in public forums and with private messaging Accordingly by submitting personal content for public posting on any of the JibJab Sites or through any of the JibJab Services you hereby waive any and all privacy expectations including the privacy expectations of any other individual who appears in your submitted content with respect to JibJab s use of such content If you do not wish to have personal content viewable by others you should not submit content for public posting on the JibJab Sites and JibJab Services</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

